@page "/"

<PageTitle>Request Portal</PageTitle>

<div class="mt-4">
    <h1>Koru Request Management</h1>
    <p>
        Use this portal to create branch requests, keep drafts up to date, and track the approval status of every submission.
        Admins can switch to the Admin Requests page to approve or reject pending work.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Users</strong> can reach <em>My Requests</em> and the <em>New Request</em> form from the navigation menu.</li>
        <li><strong>Admins</strong> oversee items waiting for action through the <em>Admin Requests</em> view.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
